OL,3,CMan and boy, 17, found guilty of
OL,4,C'mistaken identity' murder
OL,6,FA man and a 17-year-old boy have been
OL,7,Ffound guilty of murdering a man in his
OL,8,Fown garden in a case of "mistaken
OL,9,Fidentity".
OL,11,FLee Clarkson was killed at his home on
OL,12,FWest Lane, in Bishop Auckland, County
OL,13,FDurham, on 29 November last year.
OL,15,FMichael Richardson, 52, and a 17-year-
OL,16,Fold boy, who cannot be named for legal
OL,17,Freasons, were found guilty of murder
OL,18,Fat Teesside Crown Court.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G1/12
