OL,3,CMan and boy, 17, found guilty of
OL,4,C'mistaken identity' murder
OL,6,FThe court was told how Mr Clarkson,
OL,7,F41, had been dragged into his front
OL,8,Fgarden and beaten before being stabbed
OL,9,Fthree times.
OL,11,FHe died a short time later, with his
OL,12,Fcause of death being confirmed as
OL,13,Fblood loss from two of the stab wounds.
OL,15,FFollowing an investigation by Durham
OL,16,FConstabulary, five people were
OL,17,Foriginally arrested and charged with
OL,18,Fmurder.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G2/12
