OL,3,CMan and boy, 17, found guilty of
OL,4,C'mistaken identity' murder
OL,6,FMichael Richardson, 52, Karl Jones,
OL,7,F45, Helen Jones, 43, Craig Dent, 42,
OL,8,Fand a 17-year-old boy denied the
OL,9,Fcharges and underwent a seven-week
OL,10,Ftrial.
OL,12,FOn Monday 15 July, the jury found
OL,13,FRichardson, of Boddy Street, Bishop
OL,14,FAuckland, and the 17-year-old boy
OL,15,Fguilty of murder.
OL,17,FKarl Jones, of General Boucher Court,
OL,18,FBishop Auckland, was found guilty of
OL,19,Fmanslaughter but acquitted of murder.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G3/12
