OL,3,CMan and boy, 17, found guilty of
OL,4,C'mistaken identity' murder
OL,6,FDent, of Gray Street, Bishop Auckland,
OL,7,Fwas also acquitted of murder and had
OL,8,Fpreviously pleaded guilty to
OL,9,Fmanslaughter.
OL,11,FHelen Jones was found not guilty of
OL,12,Fall charges.
OL,14,FAfter the verdicts, Mr Clarkson's
OL,15,Ffamily spoke of their heartache at
OL,16,Flosing their loved one and enduring
OL,17,Fthe long trial.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G4/12
