OL,3,CMan and boy, 17, found guilty of
OL,4,C'mistaken identity' murder
OL,6,FThey said: "The fact Lee was murdered
OL,7,Fwas bad enough, but these people could
OL,8,Fhave taken responsibility from the day
OL,9,Fthey were arrested, which would have
OL,10,Fprevented us having to listen to the
OL,11,Ffinal moments of Lee's life at the
OL,12,Ftrial.
OL,14,F"This has been unbearable at times we
OL,15,Fare broken hearted, and no words can
OL,16,Fexplain the pain and torture that we
OL,17,Fhave gone through.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G5/12
