OL,3,CMan and boy, 17, found guilty of
OL,4,C'mistaken identity' murder
OL,6,F"There are no words to describe the
OL,7,Fpain, which we all feel, but we hope
OL,8,Fthat the justice served will hopefully
OL,9,Fgive us some comfort knowing the
OL,10,Fpeople responsible for the murder of
OL,11,Four Lee can't harm anyone else."
OL,13,FThe police investigation found the
OL,14,Fattackers had not intended to target
OL,15,FMr Clarkson that evening but instead
OL,16,Fset out to find Mr Clarkson's lodger,
OL,17,FSimon Blacklock, who Richardson
OL,18,Fbelieved was responsible for two
OL,19,Falleged burglaries on his house and
OL,20,Fshed.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G6/12
