OL,3,CMan and boy, 17, found guilty of
OL,4,C'mistaken identity' murder
OL,6,FOn the night of the attack, the group
OL,7,Farmed themselves with a knife, a
OL,8,Fbaseball bat and a machete and headed
OL,9,Fto the address, the court heard.
OL,11,FRichardson made several calls to Dent
OL,12,Fand the teenager earlier in the day,
OL,13,Fincluding just minutes before the
OL,14,Fattack. In a police interview, he
OL,15,Fclaimed these calls were likely to be
OL,16,Fabout his ferret and polecat breeding.
OL,18,FThe three men and the teenage boy
OL,19,Fsmashed the windows and back door of
OL,20,Fthe address in West Lane.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G7/12
