OL,3,CMan and boy, 17, found guilty of
OL,4,C'mistaken identity' murder
OL,6,FMr Clarkson heard what was going on
OL,7,Fand rushed upstairs to warn Mr
OL,8,FBlacklock, who subsequently jumped out
OL,9,Fthe window and ran off.
OL,11,FAs the group stormed in, they grabbed
OL,12,FMr Clarkson and dragged him out of the
OL,13,Fhouse into the front garden. He was
OL,14,Fthen stabbed, kicked, and punched.
OL,16,FThe teenage defendant admitted
OL,17,Fstabbing Mr Clarkson twice but claimed
OL,18,Fhe did not mean to cause him serious
OL,19,Finjury.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G8/12
