OL,3,CMan and boy, 17, found guilty of
OL,4,C'mistaken identity' murder
OL,6,FDent also admitted hitting him with a
OL,7,Fbaseball bat but said he could not
OL,8,Fremember what happened as he had taken
OL,9,Fdrugs.
OL,11,FThe court heard the group fled the
OL,12,Fscene back to a red Land Rover
OL,13,FFreelander, which was parked nearby,
OL,14,Fas Mr Clarkson was left dying.
OL,16,FNeighbours of Mr Clarkson called the
OL,17,Femergency services and rushed to help
OL,18,Fhim, but his injuries were too severe.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G9/12
