OL,3,CMan and boy, 17, found guilty of
OL,4,C'mistaken identity' murder
OL,6,FDetective Superintendent Andy
OL,7,FReynolds, Senior Investigating
OL,8,FOfficer, said: "We believe this was a
OL,9,Fcase of mistaken identity.
OL,11,F"Lee Clarkson wasn't the target that
OL,12,Fnight ` he was an innocent party in
OL,13,Fthis incident. This was a brutal
OL,14,Fattack on an innocent man in his own
OL,15,Fhome.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}       G10/12
