OL,3,CMan and boy, 17, found guilty of
OL,4,C'mistaken identity' murder
OL,6,F"The group were intent on seeking
OL,7,Fretribution that night, they armed
OL,8,Fthemselves with weapons and forced
OL,9,Ftheir way into Lee Clarkson's home.
OL,10,FSince the devastating attack they have
OL,11,Fcontinued to deny or attempt to
OL,12,Fdownplay their involvement.
OL,14,F"I am delighted the jury have seen
OL,15,Fthrough these lies and hope Lee's
OL,16,Ffamily can take some consolation in
OL,17,Fthe justice that has been administered
OL,18,Ftoday."
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}       G11/12
